    "Name": "Kodiak",
    "Details": "Though powerful, the original Kodiak lacked sufficient long range weaponry and did not come close to mounting its full compliment of armor. In 3095, saKhan Ragnar of Clan Ghost Bear tasked the technician caste with developing a variant that would resolves these setbacks. A first prototype of the new version designated V1 sported two LRM-20 and one LRM-10 launchers, an ER PPC and replaces the eight Medium Lasers with ER Small Lasers. This version also adds jump jets to the design, allowing the 'Mech to jump over 90 meters. The core concept behind this design is what eventually evolved into the Kodiak II.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Battle Fists</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.24</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
